{
  "stem": "27340.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was almost like apartheid as we knew it in South Africa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[GERMAN] and that's all right, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was water there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We could swim.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we were not allowed to go any public swimming places or cinemas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time-- I left Germany in June-- no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left Germany in March 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that-- at the age of 12, just coming on for 13.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that would be-- at the grammar school, I was there for three full years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that would be from 10 to 13 or 10 to 12 and 3/4, something--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were looking around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But like so many other Jews in Germany, who were very, very much assimilated and considered themselves firstly Germans of Mosaic persuasion-- they never denied the fact that they were Jewish, but their German nationality seemed to be predominant, as it were.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rather than saying we were Jews who happened to have German nationality, they were Germans who happened to be of Jewish religion.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, they tried to some extent-- and this is all hearsay from my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was obviously as a little child not involved in this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They tried to emigrate to various places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And every country had its quota.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Every country had its restrictions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember, for instance, had we wanted to go to France, they would've accepted us with open arms, because my parents only had two boys and France having lost so much of her manhood in the First World War, '14, '18, there were only too placed-- too pleased to replenish the young-- young males amongst their midst.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For some reason or other, this didn't materialize.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
